NAME

  Pick an expansion:

  XPLib - CrossPoint (XP) Library
  XPLib	- Extended Pascal Library
  XPLib - Cross-Platform Library

DESCRIPTION

  These are libraries that provide:

  1. a unified interface & slim layer around:
  1.1. FreePascal's os-dependent RTL (Unix, Win32)
  1.2. Delphi's RTL (Win32)
  1.3. Windows' os-specific functions (Win32)

  2. additional types and functions, e.g. TRopeStream
